# WAGER
# NOTE: gitignore does NOT support inline comments -- a '#' mid-line becomes part
# of the pattern, silently breaking the ignore. Keep every comment on its own line.
# Foundry credentials (solver side); never committed:
.env
# any env variant with secrets:
.env.*
# throwaway probes + commit-message files:
scratch/
# generated human-inspection HTML (regenerable):
reports/
# pre-audit staging battery (becomes battery.json on approval):
cases/*/battery_derived.json
# episode traces (evidence; archived outside the repo, Fable re-skin 2026-07-02):
cases/*/traces/
# EXCEPCION (Decision Log v0.66): traces EJEMPLARES citables por el paper --
# whitelist explicita por archivo; el resto de traces/ sigue fuera del repo.
!cases/latent_mix_v2/traces/
cases/latent_mix_v2/traces/*
!cases/latent_mix_v2/traces/e0_gpt-5.4_seed3.json
!cases/latent_mix_v2/traces/e0_gpt-5.4_seed2.json
!cases/latent_mix_v2/traces/e05_DeepSeek-V3.2_seed5.json
!cases/latent_mix_v2/traces/e05_gpt-5.4_seed5.json

